snippet.title: Syracuse (Odyssey 2 / Videopac) complete run - 2nd Gen Journey #32
snippet.description:
Complete run of Syracuse for the Odyssey 2 / Videopac, playing as both Archimedes and the Romans!

The 2nd Gen Journey is an exploration through all the 2nd generation video game consoles – including the Atari 2600, Intellivision and Colecovision to the arcades and the truly obscure!

See live streams of all gameplay at https://twitch.tv/hipolitopichardo
